// File Naming Rules:
// - All filenames must use kebab-case (lowercase letters, numbers, and hyphens only, e.g., "my-component.tsx").
// - Do not use camelCase, PascalCase, or underscores in filenames.

// UI Library Rules:
// - Always use DaisyUI version 5.1.12 for all interface components and styling.
// - Do not use other versions of DaisyUI or alternative UI libraries for interface elements.

// Icon Rules:
// - For all icons, use the "lucide-react" library.
// - Do not use other icon libraries (such as Heroicons, FontAwesome, etc.).

// Backend-as-a-Service (BaaS) Rules:
// - This project uses Supabase as the backend-as-a-service (BaaS) provider.

// Data Fetching Rules:
// - Always use TanStack React Query (tanstack/react-query) for all data fetching and caching in React components.
// - Do not use alternative data fetching libraries or custom hooks for server state management.
